Transparency effects are possible, but with limitations. In the case of
Wipeout, the problem is you cannot do additive blending on a Permedia
chip. We have the same problem in Heretic II, but there I was able to
emulate the feature so that it does not pop up, but the cost of this is
that some effects look different from the PC version.

